===========================
IMPORTANT – PLEASE READ
===========================

This project has been split into multiple compressed parts
because of the 25 MB upload size limit.

Please follow the steps below to access and review the project.

--------------------------------
HOW TO EXTRACT THE PROJECT
--------------------------------

1. Download ALL the files into the SAME folder.
   (Example: project.7z.001, project.7z.002, project.7z.003, etc.)

2. Install 7-Zip (if not already installed):
   https://www.7-zip.org/

3. Right-click ONLY on the first file:
      project.7z.001

4. Select:
      7-Zip → Extract Here
   or
      7-Zip → Extract to "project\"

5. The full project folder will be extracted automatically.
   (No need to extract other parts separately.)

--------------------------------
PROJECT REVIEW INSTRUCTIONS
--------------------------------

• Open the extracted folder
• Refer to the README file (if available) for project details
• The project contains:
  - Source code
  - Required resources
  - Documentation

--------------------------------
NOTE
--------------------------------

• Do NOT rename any of the split files
• Do NOT extract .002, .003 files individually
• All parts must remain in the same folder

